E"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n41819","headword_ar":"وَرِبَ","root":"wrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaworabu","text_ar":"يَوْرَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warabN","text_ar":"وَرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a root, origin, or stock, S, or a man, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, corrupt."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n41820","headword_ar":"ورّب","root":"wrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taworiybN","text_ar":"تَوْرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [app.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He expressed himself respecting a thing equivocally,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ambiguously, by words objectionable in one sense, and allowable in another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so thinks IbrD:] the inf. n. is thus explained:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano tuwar~iYa Eani","text_ar":"اَنْ تُوَرِّىَ عَنِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~aYo'i biAlmuEaAraDaAti waAlmubaAHaAti","text_ar":"الشَّىْءِ بِالمُعَارَضَاتِ وَالمُبَاحَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, K, but in the latter, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"before the last word is omitted.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n41822","headword_ar":"وَرْبٌ","root":"wrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hole of a wild beast:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aworaAbN","text_ar":"اَوْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warobN","text_ar":"وَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"space between two ribs;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA bayona AlD~ilaEayoni","text_ar":"مَا بَيْنَ الضِّلَعَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) but this (says SM) I find not in any other book than the K; and probably it should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA byn A_iSobaEayoni","text_ar":"ما بين اـِصْبَعَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"space between two fingers;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for we read in the L that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wrb","text_ar":"ورب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to signify"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mAbyn AlA^aSaAbiEi","text_ar":"مابين الاَصَابِعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aworaAbN","text_ar":"اَوْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arobN","text_ar":"اَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warobN","text_ar":"وَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"space measured by the extension of the thumb and forefinger;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fitorN","text_ar":"فِتْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aworaAbN","text_ar":"اَوْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warobN","text_ar":"وَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2934},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A member; a limb:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aworaAbN","text_ar":"اَوْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirobN","text_ar":"وِرْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[also] is a dial. from of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irobN","text_ar":"اـِرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) as signifying “ a member, or limb. ” (TA.) The form of word commonly known, says AM, is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irobN","text_ar":"اـِرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but I do not deny that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wrb","text_ar":"ورب"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be a dial. form, like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirovN","text_ar":"وِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irovN","text_ar":"اـِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are two words whereof one is a dial. form of the other. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warobN","text_ar":"وَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warobapN","text_ar":"وَرْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"podex:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isotN","text_ar":"اـِسْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aworaAbN","text_ar":"اَوْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) ―         -b3-  ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warobapN","text_ar":"وَرْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollow, that is in the lower part of the side, i. e., the hypochondre,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flank."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warobN","text_ar":"وَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mouth of the hole of a rat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mouse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^orap","text_ar":"فَاْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of a scorpion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aworaAbN","text_ar":"اَوْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n41823","headword_ar":"وِرْبٌ","root":"wrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warobN","text_ar":"وَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n41825","headword_ar":"وَرِبٌ","root":"wrb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Corrupt."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiroqN warib","text_ar":"عِرْقٌ وَرِب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A corrupt root, origin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stock."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) Aboo-Dharrah El-Hudhalee says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A_ino tanotasito tunosabo A_ilaY EiroqK waribo"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If thou mention thy lineage, thy lineage is traced up to a corrupt origin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stock"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN waribN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ وَرِبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A corrupt man."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waribN","text_ar":"وَرِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"A cloud"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is loose"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and much broken."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]}]}}